title: Rajput Indian Cuisine
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers a vegetarian & vegan section on its menu with many entree choices, including tofu veggie biryani, mushroom matar, dal makhni, chickpea masala, tofu broccoli karahi, and veg korma. A vegetarian dinner buffet is offered on the 1st Thursday of each month with a la carte menu also available. A la carte 80 items separate vegan menu also available everyday.
